Have you experienced a person, friend, family member or stranger Overdose? Unfortunately, I have and didn’t know what to do? Through help and information from my friends at www.substanceusephilly.com  @overdosepreventionphl we can all educate ourselves and save someone’s life. #Naloxone is a free, easy to use spray that can reverse an overdose. 

During the holiday season #overdoses increase dramatically and we want to help save a life.

Check out www.substanceusephilly.com @overdosepreventionphl and learn how to get your FREE #naloxone, how to administer naloxone and free #overdose prevention and reversal training.
